N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 710.8 - Report to the Justice Center

State Regulations

Upon request of the Justice Center, the program staff shall
provide a report on the activities of the committee and its panels containing
all information requested by the Justice Center. Notes
